						</div>
						<a href="#" class="publication-link">Leer artículo</a>
					</article>
					<article class="publication-card">
						<div class="publication-meta">
							<span class="publication-type">Conferencia</span>
							<span class="publication-date">2024</span>
						</div>
						<h3>AI-Driven Diagnostic Systems: A Healthcare Revolution</h3>
						<p class="publication-authors">Castro, F., Vargas, I., López, C.</p>
						<p class="publication-journal"><strong>International Conference on Medical AI</strong>, Barcelona 2024</p>
						<div class="publication-metrics">
							<span>🏆 Premio: Mejor Presentación</span>
							<span>👥 Asistentes: 500+</span>
						</div>
						<a href="#" class="publication-link">Ver presentación</a>
					</article>
					<article class="publication-card">
						<div class="publication-meta">
							<span class="publication-type">Libro</span>
							<span class="publication-date">2023</span>
						</div>
						<h3>Biotechnology and Environmental Sustainability</h3>
						<p class="publication-authors">Hernández, L., Silva, R. (Eds.)</p>
						<p class="publication-journal"><strong>Editorial UNEV Press</strong>, 328 páginas</p>
						<div class="publication-metrics">
							<span>📚 ISBN: 978-0-123456-78-9</span>
